        <header>
         <h2 class="title entry-title">
          <a href="http://policymatters.illinois.edu/study-shows-new-evidence-that-consumers-are-confused-by-date-labels-on-food-items/" rel="bookmark" title="Study shows new evidence that consumers are confused by date labels on food items">
           Study shows new evidence that consumers are confused by date labels on food items
