       <article class="post-940 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-agriculture category-environment category-policy tag-agriculture tag-conservation tag-environment-2 tag-farm-bill tag-policy">
        <header>
         <h2 class="title entry-title">
          <a href="http://policymatters.illinois.edu/conferencing-conservation-reviewing-title-ii-of-the-house-and-senate-farm-bills/" rel="bookmark" title="Conferencing Conservation: Reviewing Title II of the House and Senate Farm Bills">
           Conferencing Conservation: Reviewing Title II of the House and Senate Farm Bills
          </a>
         </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="post-meta">
         <span class="small">
          By
         </span>
         <a class="author url fn" href="http://policymatters.illinois.edu/author/jcoppess/" rel="author" title="Posts by Jonathan Coppess">
          Jonathan Coppess
         </a>
